Reliance Capital May Sell Stake in AMC Unit to Nippon, CNBC Says

-- B y   H a r i   G o v i n d
-- 
2011-09-27T05:58:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/reliance-capital-may-sell-stake-in-amc-unit-to-nippon-cnbc-says.html
Reliance Capital Ltd. (RCAPT)  is in
“advanced talks” to sell a stake in its asset management unit
to Japan’s Nippon Life Insurance Co., the CNBC television
reported today, citing Chairman  Anil Ambani .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Hari Govind at 
 hgovind@bloomberg.net  